subpara.para:
A complete set of Service Bulletins is procurable
using Part No. 3027557 for PT6A-38 engines, 3026526 for PT6A-41 engines,
and 3020780 for PT6A-42/42A engines.

procedure.step:
Install starter (PWC31207)
on accessory gearbox housing studs; secure with four nuts and washers;
torque 150 to 170 lb.in.
